{"type":"message","id":"5cbdc8eb","parentId":"31a9471d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T23:29:16.936Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 07:29 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请搜索以下行业的最新动态（2026年3月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n请查找最近的行业新闻、政策、技术趋势、市场动态等信息，整理3-5条最关键的发现。"}],"timestamp":1773962956933}}
{"type":"message","id":"57a16f86","parentId":"5cbdc8eb","timestamp":"2026-03-19T23:29:21.712Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我搜索4个行业的最新动态（2026年3月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n我需要搜索这些行业的最新新闻、政策、技术趋势、市场动态等信息，并整理3-5条最关键的发现。\n\n我应该使用 web-search skill 来进行搜索。让我先读取这个技能的说明。","thinkingSignature":"9e71fe46c67538a4a50924062dcfc906996c687f5699f59415d80185e2926d2b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b0l9m6rphn0g_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117,"output":120,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":30718,"totalTokens":30955,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.000144,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0036861599999999995,"total":0.0038652599999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773962956934}}
{"type":"message","id":"78cf2b25","parentId":"57a16f86","timestamp":"2026-03-19T23:29:21.717Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_b0l9m6rphn0g_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773962961714}}
